channel.title: Vps is setup, but its not online
channel.description:
Okay so I bought this like 4 days ago, and everything is set up, the server is running, and everything is good. So I've tried logging on, but it wont let me...Says its offline on status checker too. When I bought the vps it said pick a domain name.
Domain Name: server1.miscpk.com And the serial says its online, so what do I do to make it online and available to play...

item.title: Vps is setup, but its not online
item.dc:creator: @KempiScape KempiScape
item.description:
@KempiScape wrote:

God damnit, first of all its not a domain name.
Second of all, look for your firewalls. Still not fine? Contact your VPS host.
